OL,3,CProposition to remove Jersey's Bailiff
OL,4,Cfrom States Assembly lodged
OL,6,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister has
OL,7,Fproposed to remove the Bailiff from
OL,8,FJersey's States Assembly.
OL,10,FIn his proposition, Deputy Andy Jehan
OL,11,Fsays this decision would "establish
OL,12,Fthe important principle of the
OL,13,FSeparation of Powers."
OL,15,FIt follows Jersey's Bailiff, Sir
OL,16,FTimothy Le Cocq, announcing his
OL,17,Fretirement from office in October.
OL,19,FIf approved, the removal would also
OL,20,Fintroduce two new States Assembly
OL,21,Froles.
