OL,6,FDeputy Andy Jehan is now calling for
OL,7,Fthe States Assembly to be able to
OL,8,Fselect its own Speaker and Deputy
OL,9,FSpeaker.
OL,11,FRules of the new roles would involve
OL,12,Facting impartially at all times, being
OL,13,Funable to lodge propositions, table
OL,14,Fquestions, participate in debates, or
OL,15,Fvote on propositions.
