OL,3,CProposition to remove Jersey's Bailiff
OL,4,Cfrom States Assembly lodged
OL,6,FThe Deputy Speaker should be required
OL,7,Fto act impartially when chairing
OL,8,Fmeetings of the Assembly and
OL,9,Fundertaking official duties related to
OL,10,Ftheir role as Deputy Speaker.
OL,12,FWhen not acting as Deputy Speaker, the
OL,13,FMember elected to this position may
OL,14,Fcontinue to lodge propositions, table
OL,15,Fquestions, participate in debates,
OL,16,Fvote on propositions and sit on
OL,17,FScrutiny panels.
